Frequently Asked Questions
How long does it take to see results from a lead generation partnership?

Most campaigns begin showing early indicators within the first thirty to sixty days, with pipeline momentum building significantly over three to six months as targeting is refined and messaging is optimized. Sustainable growth comes from sustained investment.

Is outsourced lead generation a good fit for small and mid-sized businesses?

Absolutely. In fact, smaller businesses often benefit the most from a lead generation partner because they gain access to enterprise-grade capabilities without the overhead of building an internal team. It allows them to compete effectively against larger competitors.

What makes intent-based lead generation different from traditional approaches?

Traditional lead generation often targets broad audiences based on demographic or firmographic data. Intent-based lead generation adds a behavioral layer, identifying prospects who are actively researching solutions like yours. This results in significantly higher engagement rates and faster pipeline velocity.

How does content syndication contribute to lead generation?

Content syndication places your thought leadership content in front of targeted audiences across trusted industry platforms. Prospects who engage with your content have already demonstrated interest in the subject matter, making them warmer, more qualified leads than those reached through purely outbound channels.

